sage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brautigam has now addressed the situation, with the British Dressage boss calling for people to 'be kind' to Durjardin.\", \"from\": 5811, \"to\": 5930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5863, \"end\": 5879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also suggested that the leak had been intended to damage her career, too.\", \"from\": 5932, \"to\": 6008, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a letter to members publicised last night, he said: \\\"I do find claims that this was done to 'save dressage' somewhat disingenuous, given that it was timed to cause maximum damage to our sport.\", \"from\": 6009, \"to\": 6204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Mike Tyson 'is in no fit state' as Jake Paul receives alternative offer after Mike Perry win  \\\"However, what will save dressage is how we all respond to this crisis by demonstrating our love and care for horses.\\\"\", \"from\": 6206, \"to\": 6428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6251, \"end\": 6260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jake Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\"}, {\"begin\": 6294, \"end\": 6304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Perry_(fighter)\", \"score\": 0.895862561827038, \"rank\": 0.11512791991102501, \"text\": \"Mike Perry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Perry_(fighter)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Perry_(fighter)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brautigam also condemned the actions of Durjardin, adding: \\\"Let me be clear: the actions we have witnessed in that video are completely unacceptable.\", \"from\": 6430, \"to\": 6579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have all been shocked and appalled by this indefensible conduct.\", \"from\": 6581, \"to\": 6649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As I have always said, the horse is at the heart of everything we do in British Dressage, and equine welfare must always be paramount above all other considerations.\\\"\", \"from\": 6651, \"to\": 6818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6724, \"end\": 6740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LATEST SPORTS NEWS:  On the eve of the official opening of the Paris 2024 Olympics, members are invited to read a personal message shared this evening from our Chief Executive Jason Brautigam, reflecting on what this week's challenges mean for us and the future of our sport.https://t.co/vkz55QZwSqpic.twitter.com/OZ2bI6md84  Brautigam does say Durjardin has done the right thing by fronting up and apologising, however.\", \"from\": 6820, \"to\": 7240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6996, \"end\": 7001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Grimshaw\", \"score\": 0.999991020778748, \"rank\": 7.645494979584507e-06, \"text\": \"Jason\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Grimshaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Grimshaw\"}, {\"begin\": 7103, \"end\": 7107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"t.co\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Charlotte Dujardin has done the right thing by accepting responsibility and expressing remorse,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 7242, \"to\": 7349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7243, \"end\": 7261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While we do not condone her behaviour, we must remember that there is also a human element to this - and, regardless of what has happened, she still deserves our understanding.\", \"from\": 7351, \"to\": 7528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Please be kind and bear in mind that we have a duty of care in our interactions with one another.\\\"\", \"from\": 7530, \"to\": 7629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics: Charlotte Dujardin has apologised for her actions  GETTY  Durjardin has been slapped with a provisional six-month ban for her actions.\", \"from\": 7631, \"to\": 7775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7641, \"end\": 7659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has also been axed by a horse and donkey charity, with two equestrian sponsors parting ways with the 39-year-old as well.\", \"from\": 7777, \"to\": 7902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7840, \"end\": 7850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9699570326493742, \"rank\": 0.030973079057076316, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}]}]}"